solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public ListNode deleteDuplicates(ListNode head) {--newline--            if(head == null || head.next == null)return head;--newline--            head.next = deleteDuplicates(head.next);--newline--            return head.val == head.next.val ? head.next : head;--newline--    }--newline--    --newline--}
